title: Readout of President Obama's call with British Prime Minister Cameron | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
August 25, 2010

 



Readout of President Obama's call with British Prime Minister Cameron




President Obama called the Prime Minister earlier today to offer his congratulations to the Prime Minister and Mrs. Cameron on the birth of their daughter.   The President and Prime Minister also took the opportunity to compare notes on the Middle East.
